9a3c7fdc-1f33-4e35-bc0d-6035b585b0c7.description: By implementing our Create Student Hold process, your business can streamline hold creation, improve communication between stakeholders, and ensure efficient management of student holds. It eliminates manual processes, reduces errors, and enhances transparency in hold management, ultimately improving the overall student experience and administrative efficiency.
